        <problem id="fs-id1169736693588">
          <para id="import-auto-id1169736581639">Find the minimum thickness of a soap bubble that appears red when illuminated by white light perpendicular to its surface. Take the wavelength to be 680 nm, and assume the same index of refraction as water.</para>
