      <exercise id="fs-id1169736675909" type="problems-exercises">
        <problem id="fs-id1169737713781">
          <para id="import-auto-id1169737787716">A film of soapy water (<m:math><m:mrow><m:mrow><m:mrow><m:mrow><m:mi>n</m:mi><m:mo stretchy="false">=</m:mo><m:mn>1</m:mn></m:mrow><m:mtext>.</m:mtext><m:mtext>33</m:mtext></m:mrow></m:mrow></m:mrow></m:math>) on top of a plastic cutting board has a thickness of 233 nm. What color is most strongly reflected if it is illuminated perpendicular to its surface?</para>
